4.94/5  rDev +10.8%look: 5 | smell: 4.75 | taste: 5 | feel: 5 |  overall: 5On tap at Surly. The color is beautiful, glowing, slightly hazy orange with a white head. Smell is fantastic tropical fruit. Taste is perfectly balanced bitter and sweet citrus and tropical fruits. 
