It's semi-dry with medium carbonation, light to medium body. Thin texture. Highly drinkable. In general it’s like good, very very juicy session-beer, really nice combination of malts and US hops. The bitterness could be higher (it’s AIPA), but still worth trying. Another good beer from Amager in collab. with Surly. 705 charactersBlazerT, Jan 02, 2015
